Title: Panther's Quest
Director: Sebastian Montes, Ciro Nieli, Frank Paur
Actors: Brian Bloom, Colleen O'Shaughnessey, Eric Loomis, Wally Wingert
Plot: The Black Panther seeks the Avengers' aid in freeing his African nation of Wakanda from usurper king Man-Ape, and stopping Hydra agents Ulysses Klaw and the Grim Reaper from stealing Wakanda's supply of vibranium.
